rows.name:
A rumor here, a rumor there ♪
Welm loves gossip every-which-where!

rows.label: qst004005_msg0002
rows.name:
Looking for info about whoever
destroyed the crane, are you? Well,
of course I've heard a thing or two!

rows.label: qst004005_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard some Driver say they saw
two suspicious shadows by the tree
on the outskirts of town.

rows.label: qst004005_msg0004
rows.name:
You think it might've been
criminals scoping the place out?

rows.label: qst004005_msg0005
rows.name:
No way! I don't wanna think about that!
The world's a scary enough place for
a girl like me!

rows.label: qst004005_msg0101
rows.name:
A rumor here, a rumor there ♪
Welm loves gossip every-which-where!

rows.label: qst004005_msg0102
rows.name:
I hear Pettle-kun's sooo impressed
by Rahim, the guard, he keeps
pretending he's him!
